renice]]'' (1976) \n*[[1978 in film|1978]] ''[[El lugar sin l\u00edmites (film)|El lugar sin l\u00edmites]]'' (1978); ''[[Naufragio]]'' (1978) \n*[[1979 in film|1979]] ''[[Cadena perpetua]]'' (1979) \n*[[1980 in film|1980]] ''[[El a\u00f1o de la peste]]'' (1979) \n*[[1981 in film|1981]] ''[[Las grandes aguas]]'' (1980) \n*[[1982 in film|1982]] ''[[Ora s\u00ed tenemos que ganar]]'' (1981) \n*[[1983 in film|1983]] ''[[La pachanga]]'' (1982) \n*[[1984 in film|1984]] ''[[Bajo la metralla]]'' (1983) \n*[[1985 in film|1985]] ''[[Frida, naturaleza viva]]'' (1986) \n*[[1986 in film|1986]] ''[[Veneno para las hadas]]'' (1984) \n*[[1987 in film|1987]] ''[[El imperio de la fortuna]]'' (1986) \n*[[1988 in film|1988]] ''[[Mariana, Mariana]]'' (1987) \n*[[1989 in film|1989]] ''[[Esperanza (film)|Esperanza]]'' (1988) \n*[[1990 in film|1990]] ''[[Goitia, un dios para s\u00ed mismo]]'' (1988) \n*[[1991 in film|1991]] ''[[Rojo amanecer]]'' (1989) \n*[[1992 in film|1992]] ''[[Like Water for Chocolate (film)|Como agua para chocolate]]'' (1992) \n*[[1993 in film|1993]] ''[[Cronos (film)|Cronos]]'' (1993) \n*[[1994 in film|1994]] ''[[Principio y fin]]'' (1993) \n*[[1995 in film|1995]] ''[[El callej\u00f3n de los milagros]]'' (1995) \n*[[1996 in film|1996]] ''[[Sin remitente]]'' (1995) \n*[[1997 in film|1997]] ''[[Cilantro y perejil]]'' (1995) \n*[[1998 in film|1998]] ''[[Por si no te vuelvo a ver]]'' (1997) \n*[[1999 in film|1999]] ''[[Bajo California: El l\u00edmite del tiempo]]'' (1998) \n*[[2000 in film|2000]] ''[[La ley de Herodes]]'' (1999) \n*[[2001 in film|2001]] ''[[Amores perros]]'' (2000) \n*[[2002 in film|2002]] ''[[Cuentos de hadas para dormir cocodrilos]]'' (2002) \n*[[2003 in film|2003]] ''[[El crimen del padre Amaro]]'' (2002) \n*[[2004 in film|2004]] ''[[El misterio del Trinidad]]'' (2003) \n*[[2005 in film|2005]] ''[[Temporada de patos]]'' (2004) \n*[[2006 in film|2006]] ''[[Mezcal]]'' (2004) \n*[[2007 in film|2007]] ''[[Pan's Labyrinth|El laberinto del fauno]]'' (2006) \n*[[2008 in film|2008]] ''[[Stellet Licht]]'' (2007) \n*[[2009 in film|2009]] ''[[Lake Tahoe (film)|Lake Tahoe]]'' (2008) \n\n===2010s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!width=\"100\"|'''Year'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''English title'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''Original title'''\n!width=\"300\"|'''Director'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[52nd Ariel Awards|2010]]<br /><small>[[52nd Ariel Awards|(52nd)]]</small>\n|-style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n|''[[Nora's Will]]''||''Cinco d\u00edas sin Nora''||[[Mariana Chenillo]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''Coraz\u00f3n del Tiempo''||Alberto Cort\u00e9s \n|-\n|''Northless''||''Norteado ''||Rigoberto P\u00e9rezcano \n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[53rd Ariel Awards|2011]]<br /><small>[[53rd Ariel Awards|(53rd)]]</small>\n|-style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Hell (2010 film)|El Infierno]]''||[[Luis Estrada (director)|Luis Estrada]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''Abel''||[[Diego Luna]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''Chico Grande''||[[Felipe Cazals]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[54th Ariel Awards|2012]]<br /><small>[[54th Ariel Awards|(54th)]]</small>\n|-style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Pastorela (2011 film)|Pastorela]]''||Emilio Portes\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Miss Bala (2011 film)|Miss Bala]]''||Gerardo Naranjo \n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[D\u00edas de gracia]]''||Everardo Gout \n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[55th Ariel Awards|2013]]<br /><small>[[55th Ariel Awards|(55th)]]</small>\n|-style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n|''[[The Prize (2011 film)|The Prize]]''||''El premio''||Paula Markovitch\n|-\n|''[[The Delay]]''||''La demora''||[[Rodrigo Pl\u00e1]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"|''[[Los \u00daltimos Cristeros]]''||Mat\u00edas Meyer\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[56th Ariel Awards|2014]]<br /><small>[[56th Ariel Awards|(56th)]]</small>\n|-style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" \n|''[[The Golden Dream]]''||''La jaula de oro''||Diego Quemada-D\u00edez\n|-\n|colspan