:Ariel Awards]]\n", "text_old": "The '''Ariel Award for Best Picture''' ('''Ariel de Mejor Pel\u00edcula''' in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]) is the highest award given in [[Mexico]] to a single [[film]] and is part of the [[Mexican Academy of Film]]'s [[Ariel Award]] program.\n\n==Award results<ref name=\"imdb-results\">[https://www.imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Ariel_Awards_Mexico/ Event Summary of Ariel Awards, Mexico], [[Internet Movie Database]]</ref>==\n*[[1946 in film|1946]] ''[[The Shack (1945 film)|La barraca]]'' (1945)\n*[[1947 in film|1947]] ''[[Enamorada (film)|Enamorada]]'' (1946) \n*[[1948 in film|1948]] ''[[La perla (film)|La perla]]'' (1947) \n*[[1949 in film|1949]] ''[[R\u00edo Escondido (film)|R\u00edo escondido]]'' (1948) \n*[[1950 in film|1950]] ''[[Una familia de tantas]]'' (1949) \n*[[1951 in film|1951]] ''[[Los olvidados]]'' (1950) \n*[[1952 in film|1952]] ''[[En la palma de tu mano]]'' (1951) \n:[[1953 in film|1953]] &mdash; Not awarded\n*[[1954 in film|1954]] ''[[El ni\u00f1o y la niebla]]'' (1953) \n*[[1955 in film|1955]] ''[[Los Fern\u00e1ndez de Peralvillo]]'' (1954) \n*[[1956 in film|1956]] ''[[Robinson Crusoe (1954 film)|Robinson Crusoe]]'' (1954) \n*[[1957 in film|1957]] ''[[El camino de la vida]]'' (1956) \n*[[1958 in film|1958]] ''[[Tizoc (film)|Tizoc]]'' (1957) \n:[[1959 in film|1959]] to [[1971 in film|1971]] &mdash; Awards suspended\n*[[1972 in film|1972]] ''[[Las puertas del para\u00edso]]'' (1971); ''[[T\u00fa, yo, nosotros]]'' (1972); ''[[El \u00e1guila descalza]]'' (1971) \n*[[1973 in film|1973]] ''[[The Castle of Purity|El castillo de la pureza]]'' (1973); ''[[Mec\u00e1nica nacional]]'' (1972); ''[[Reed, M\u00e9xico insurgente]]'' (1973) \n*[[1974 in film|1974]] ''[[El principio]]'' (1973) \n*[[1975 in film|1975]] ''[[La choca]]'' (1974); ''[[La otra virginidad]]'' (1975) \n*[[1976 in film|1976]] ''[[Letters from Marusia|Actas de Marusia]]'' (1976) \n*[[1977 in film|1977]] ''[[La pasi\u00f3n seg\u00fan Berenice]]'' (1976) \n*[[1978